data.description: THIS IS A WORKFORCE HOUSING PROPERTY: INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY & BUYER CAN NOT HAVE OWNED A PROPERTY WITHIN THE PAST 3 YRS. Come see this beautiful 3 story townhouse available in Downtown Delray Beach, easily within walking distance to everything. All of downtown Delray is just outside your front door, walk to the restaurants, shops, even the beach. The CODA community is located directly behind the Delray Beach library, and current ongoing Sundy Village development. This home is priced below market value and per the deed restrictions, cannot be sold for more than the asking price. Income and maximum mortgage payment restrictions apply. Down payment assistance is also available. Please reach out to the Delray Beach neighborhood services division for eligibility.
